024 | Laravel | Nov 2024**\\n\\u2022 Developed a web application to display real-time quick count results, achieving 95% accuracy in data processing *[estimasi]*\\n\\u2022 Implemented backend systems using Laravel, supporting efficient data integration for 10,000+ users *[estimasi]*\\n\\n**Airseat | React.js | Jul 2024**\\n\\u2022 Developed a web-based airline ticket booking system, streamlining the booking process for 500+ users per month *[estimasi]*\\n\\u2022 Created detailed system documentation, including diagrams and testing documents, improving team collaboration *[estimasi]*\\n\\n**InfoMATIC | Nov 2023**\\n\\u2022 Developed an intuitive dashboard to effectively monitor and visualize students\\u2019 academic performance, increasing usage by 50% *[estimasi]*\\n\\u2022 Produced comprehensive system documentation, ensuring clarity and quality assurance for future developers *[estimasi]*\\n\\n**Library Information System | Laravel | Oct 2023**\\n\\u2022 Developed the system using Laravel and Next.js, managing over 1,000 books and 500 members *[estimasi]*\\n\\u2022 Created system documentation (SRS) and system design, improving future maintenance efficiency *[estimasi]*\"},\"rencana_aksi\":[\"Langkah 1: Revisi profil untuk menekankan pengalaman dan pencapaian yang relevan.\",\"Langkah 2: Tambahkan data kuantitatif pada setiap pengalaman kerja dan proyek.\",\"Langkah 3: Perkuat keterampilan dengan menonjolkan yang paling relevan untuk posisi yang dilamar.\",\"Langkah 4: Tulis ulang alasan perubahan untuk memberikan konteks yang lebih baik.\",\"Langkah 5: Pastikan format dan struktur CV konsisten dan mudah dibaca.\"]}','2026-04-28 09:03:31','2026-04-28 09:03:31'),
