borated with 5 cross-functional teams to translate business requirements into system features, improving project delivery time by 25% *[estimasi]*\\n\\u2022 Prepared system documentation (SRS, ERD) and validated requirements, ensuring clarity for 10+ stakeholders *[estimasi]*\\n\\n**Full Stack Web Developer | Independent Study (Kampus Merdeka) | Feb 2024 - Jun 2024**\\n\\u2022 Developed 4 scalable web applications using modern technologies, including React.js and Node.js, achieving a 30% increase in user engagement *[estimasi]*\\n\\u2022 Produced comprehensive workflow documentation and functional specifications to support development, enhancing team collaboration effectiveness by 40% *[estimasi]*\\n\\u2022 Implemented Agile practices, leading to a 20% improvement in project delivery timelines *[estimasi]*\\n\\n**Computer Lab Assistant on Database | Aug 2023 \\u2013 Dec 2024**\\n\\u2022 Mentored 20+ students in database concepts, improving their practical implementation skills by 30% *[estimasi]*\\n\\u2022 Provided technical support during lab sessions, resolving 15+ technical issues weekly *[estimasi]*\\n\\u2022 Assessed assignments and delivered constructive feedback, resulting in a 25% improvement in student performance *[estimasi]*\"},\"pengalaman_organisasi\":{\"alasan_perubahan\":\"TraKerja merekomendasikan untuk memperkuat pengalaman organisasi dengan menambahkan action verbs yang lebih dinamis dan data kuantitatif yang menunjukkan dampak dari kontribusi kandidat. Ini akan membantu perekrut melihat kemampuan kandidat dalam memimpin dan berkontribusi dalam konteks organisasi.\",\"teks_revisi\":\"**Coordinator of Art and Decoration | Informatics Gathering | Dec 2022**\\n\\u2022 Led a decoration team of 5 members, ensuring visual concepts aligned with the event theme, enhancing participant satisfaction by 30% *[estimasi]*\\n\\u2022 Developed 10+ creative decoration ideas to enhance participant experience, resulting in positive feedback from 90% of attendees *[estimasi]*\\n\\u2022 Coordinated with 3 committees to ensure smooth event execution, reducing logistical issues by 20% *[estimasi]*\\n\\n**Liaison Officer | Annual Informatics Competition | Sep 2023**\\n\\u2022 Managed communication between 2 organizers and 100+ participants effectively, ensuring timely responses to inquiries *[estimasi]*\\n\\u2022 Ensured smooth coordination and timely response to participant needs, improving overall event satisfaction by 25% *[estimasi]*\\n\\n**Staff of Public Relations | Entrepreneur Talkshow | Sep 2022**\\n\\u2022 Coordinated with 5 speakers and cross-functional event teams, ensuring seamless event execution with zero delays *[estimasi]*\\n\\u2022 Successfully secured sponsorships from 5+ partners through effective communication and negotiation, increasing event budget by 40% *[estimasi]*\\n\\u2022 Contributed to increasing event attendance to over 100 participants through strategic promotion and collaboration, achieving a 50% increase from the previous year *[estimasi]*\"},\"prestasi_dan_publikasi\":{\"alasan_perubahan\":\"TraKerja merekomendasikan untuk menambahkan konteks pada setiap sertifikasi yang diperoleh, termasuk institusi dan tanggal, untuk memberikan gambaran yang lebih jelas tentang kredibilitas dan komitmen kandidat terhadap pengembangan profesional.\",\"teks_revisi\":\"\\u2022 Backend Developer Certification from CTARSA Foundation \\u2013 Detikcom, Dec 2024\\n\\u2022 Full Stack Web Developer Certification \\u2013 Binar Academy, Jun 2024\\n\\u2022 Database Programming with PL\\/SQL \\u2013 Oracle Academy, Jun 2023\\n\\u2022 Database Programming with SQL \\u2013 Oracle Academy, Jun 2023\"},\"profil\":{\"alasan_perubahan\":\"TraKerja merekomendasikan perbaikan pada profil dengan menambahkan informasi tentang pengalaman dan pencapaian yang relevan, serta menekankan komitmen terhadap pembelajaran berkelanjutan. Hal ini memberikan gambaran yang lebih kuat tentang nilai yang dapat dibawa kandidat ke perusahaan.\",\"teks_revisi\":\"Computer Science graduate with 2+ years of experience in Software Development, Data Analytics, and Quality Assurance. Proven ability to enhance system performance and improve user experience through effective testing and development practices. Committed to continuous learning and leveraging technology to drive business success.\"},\"projek\":{\"alasan_perubahan\":\"TraKerja merekomendasikan untuk memperkuat deskripsi proyek dengan menambahkan action verbs yang kuat dan data kuantitatif untuk menunjukkan dampak dari proyek yang telah dikerjakan. Ini akan membantu perekrut memahami kontribusi konkret kandidat dalam setiap proyek.\",\"teks_revisi\":\"**Quick Count Pilkada 2024 | Laravel, MySQL | Nov 2024**\\n\\u2022 Developed a web application to display real-time quick count results, achieving 99% accuracy in data processing *[estimasi]*\\n\\u2022 Implemented backend systems using Laravel, supporting efficient data integration for over 10,000 users *[estimasi]*\\n\\n**Airseat | React.js, PostgreSQL | Jul 2024**\\n\\u2022 Developed a web-based airline ticket booking system, streamlining booking processes for 1,000+ users *[estimasi]*\\n\\u2022 Created detailed system documentation, including diagrams and testing documents, ensuring clarity for future development *[estimasi]*\\n\\n**InfoMATIC | Web Application | Nov 2023**\\n\\u2022 Developed an intuitive dashboard to effectively monitor and visualize students\\u2019 academic performance, improving user engagement by 30% *[estimasi]*\\n\\u2022 Produced comprehensive system documentation, including system diagrams and testing artifacts, ensuring quality assurance *[estimasi]*\\n\\n**Library Information System | Laravel, Next.js | Oct 2023**\\n\\u2022 Developed the system using Laravel for backend API and Next.js for front-end, managing over 500 book records *[estimasi]*\\n\\u2022 Created system documentation (SRS) and system design (use case and class diagrams), enhancing project clarity *[estimasi]*\"},\"rencana_aksi\":[\"Langkah 1: Perbarui CV dengan menambahkan data kuantitatif pada setiap pengalaman dan proyek.\",\"Langkah 2: Ganti semua bullet points dengan action verbs yang kuat dari daftar Harvard.\",\"Langkah 3: Sesuaikan profil dengan menyoroti pencapaian yang relevan dan tujuan karier.\",\"Langkah 4: Organisir keterampilan dalam kategori yang jelas dan relevan dengan posisi yang dilamar.\",\"Langkah 5: Siapkan dokumen pendukung yang menunjukkan proyek dan pencapaian yang telah dilakukan.\"]}','2026-04-28 09:23:07','2026-04-28 09:23:07'),
(68,4,'📢 JOB VACANCY\r\nIT Field Support Officer\r\n\r\nJob Overview:\r\nIT Field Support Officer bertanggung jawab untuk menangani berbagai isu terkait IT, baik secara on-site maupun remote. \r\n\r\nKey Responsibilities:\r\n* Memberikan dukungan end-user (helpdesk, troubleshooting Tier 1 & 2) untuk masalah hardware, software, dan jaringan\r\n* Melakukan setup, konfigurasi, dan perbaikan dasar perangkat (printer, scanner, mouse, keyboard, monitor, dll.)\r\n* Menangani permasalahan jaringan serta menyediakan koneksi wired dan wireless\r\n* Mendiagnosis dan memperbaiki masalah hardware yang lebih kompleks, termasuk penggantian komponen\r\n* Berkoordinasi dengan vendor untuk klaim garansi dan perbaikan lanjutan\r\n* Melakukan monitoring jaringan (NOC) serta pemeliharaan yang diperlukan\r\n* Menyediakan dukungan on-call dan troubleshooting jarak jauh untuk isu mendesak\r\n* Mengikuti prosedur manajemen insiden dan melakukan eskalasi bila diperlukan\r\n* Menyusun dan memperbarui dokumentasi terkait proses sistem dan troubleshooting\r\n\r\nMore info:\r\nhttps://karir.batangkab.go.id/vacancies/3874','CV-Zhafira Amanda (Eng Ver).pdf','{\"keterampilan\":{\"alasan_perubahan\":\"TraKerja merekomendasikan penataan ulang keterampilan dengan membagi menjadi kategori yang jelas untuk memudahkan pembaca dalam menilai kualifikasi. Ini juga akan membantu menonjolkan keterampilan yang paling relevan dengan posisi yang dilamar.\",\"teks_revisi\":\"**Soft Skills:** Teamwork, Time Management, Organizational Skills, Communication, Analytical Thinking, Problem Solving, Stakeholder Management.\\n**Hard Skills:** Quality Assurance & Software Testing (Manual Testing, Test Case, Bug Reporting, Regression Testing), SDLC & Agile, Business Analysis, Requirement Documentation (SRS, Use Case), UML & ERD.\\n**Tech Skills:** SQL, Python, JavaScript, Java, HTML\\/CSS, Laravel, React.js, Next.js, PHP, Databases (MySQL, MongoDB, PostgreSQL), UI\\/UX.\\n**Tools:** Figma, Miro, Notion, Trello, Microsoft Office, Lucidchart\\/Draw.io, Git, Postman API, Looker Studio.\"},\"pendidikan\":{\"alasan_perubahan\":\"TraKerja merekomendasikan penambahan detail pada pendidikan dengan menyoroti kursus yang relevan dan pencapaian akademik. Ini akan membantu menunjukkan kualifikasi yang lebih kuat dan relevansi dengan posisi yang dilamar.\",\"teks_revisi\":\"**Universitas Diponegoro | Computer Science | Aug 2021 \\u2013 Feb 2025**\\n\\u2022 Completed relevant coursework in Software Engineering, Machine Learning, and Databases, enhancing technical expertise.\\n\\u2022 Engaged in multiple software projects, applying theoretical knowledge to practical applications.\\n\\n**SMA Negeri 1 Jakarta | IPA | 2018**\\n\\u2022 Graduated with honors, achieving a GPA of 3.8\\/4.0.\"},\"pengalaman_kerja\":{\"alasan_perubahan\":\"TraKerja merekomendasikan penguatan seluruh bullet points di section pengalaman kerja dengan tiga pendekatan utama: (1) mengganti kata kerja pasif dengan action verbs aktif dari Harvard untuk menunjukkan hasil yang lebih baik; (2) menambahkan estimasi data kuantitatif pada setiap bullet point untuk memberikan konteks yang lebih jelas tentang pencapaian; (3) menonjolkan aspek teknis yang relevan dengan job description untuk menarik perhatian recruiter.\",\"teks_revisi\":\"**Quality Assurance Intern | Telkom Indonesia | Nov 2025 - Present**\\n\\u2022 Performed manual testing on 5+ web applications, including the PaDi UMKM system, ensuring system quality and usability, resulting in a 30% reduction in user-reported issues *[estimasi]*.\\n\\u2022 Designed and executed 20+ test cases while documenting and tracking 50+ bugs systematically, improving testing efficiency by 25% *[estimasi]*.\\n\\u2022 Collaborated with a team of 4 developers to validate fixes and conducted regression testing before release, ensuring timely product launches.\\n\\n**Backend Developer Intern | Detikcom | Sep 2024 - Dec 2024**\\n\\u2022 Developed and deployed 3+ web applications using Laravel, PHP, and MySQL, serving over 1,000 users *[estimasi]*.\\n\\u2022 Collaborated with cross-functional teams to translate business requirements into system features, enhancing user satisfaction by 20% *[estimasi]*.\\n\\u2022 Prepared system documentation (SRS, ERD) and validated requirements, ensuring clarity and alignment with project goals.\\n\\n**Full Stack Web Developer | Independent Study (Kampus Merdeka) | Feb 2024 - Jun 2024**\\n\\u2022 Developed scalable web applications using modern technologies, including HTML, CSS, JavaScript, Node.js, and React.js, achieving a 40% increase in user engagement *[estimasi]*.\\n\\u2022 Produced comprehensive workflow documentation and detailed functional specifications to support development, improving team communication.\\n\\u2022 Implemented Agile practices, including sprint planning and backlog prioritization, resulting in a 15% increase in project delivery speed *[estimasi]*.\\n\\n**Computer Lab Assistant on Database | Aug 2023 \\u2013 Dec 2024**\\n\\u2022 Mentored 20+ students in database concepts (SQL, ERD), enhancing their practical implementation skills and improving overall class performance by 30% *[estimasi]*.\\n\\u2022 Provided technical support and solutions during lab sessions, resolving 15+ issues weekly *[estimasi]*.\\n\\u2022 Assessed assignments and delivered constructive feedback to improve student understanding, contributing to a 25% increase in assignment scores *[estimasi]*.\"},\"pengalaman_organisasi\":{\"alasan_perubahan\":\"TraKerja merekomendasikan penguatan bullet points di pengalaman organisasi dengan menambahkan action verbs yang lebih kuat dan data kuantitatif untuk menunjukkan dampak yang lebih jelas dari kontribusi yang diberikan. Ini akan membantu menunjukkan kemampuan kepemimpinan dan organisasi yang relevan dengan posisi yang dilamar.\",\"teks_revisi\":\"**Coordinator of Art and Decoration | Informatics Gathering | Dec 2022**\\n\\u2022 Led a team of 5 in the decoration process, ensuring visual concepts aligned with the event theme, enhancing participant experience by 30% *[estimasi]*.\\n\\u2022 Developed 10+ creative decoration ideas to enhance the event atmosphere, contributing to positive feedback from 90% of participants *[estimasi]*.\\n\\u2022 Coordinated with 3 committees to ensure smooth event execution, leading to a successful gathering with over 150 attendees *[estimasi]*.\\n\\n**Liaison Officer | Annual Informatics Competition | Sep 2023**\\n\\u2022 Managed communication between organizers and 100+ participants effectively, ensuring timely responses to participant needs, improving satisfaction rates by 25% *[estimasi]*.\\n\\u2022 Ensured smooth coordination during the event, leading to a 15% increase in participant engagement compared to previous years *[estimasi]*.\\n\\n**Staff of Public Relations | Entrepreneur Talkshow | Sep 2022**\\n\\u2022 Coordinated with 5+ speakers and cross-functional event teams to ensure seamless event execution, resulting in a successful event attended by over 100 participants *[estimasi]*.\\n\\u2022 Successfully secured sponsorships from 5+ partners through effective communication and negotiation, increasing event budget by 40% *[estimasi]*.\\n\\u2022 Contributed to increasing event attendance by 30% through strategic promotion and collaboration with local organizations *[estimasi]*.\"},\"prestasi_dan_publikasi\":{\"alasan_perubahan\":\"TraKerja merekomendasikan penambahan konteks pada sertifikasi untuk menunjukkan relevansi dan nilai dari setiap pencapaian. Ini akan membantu memperkuat kredibilitas kandidat di mata recruiter.\",\"teks_revisi\":\"\\u2022 Backend Developer Certification from CTARSA Foundation \\u2013 Detikcom, Dec 2024.\\n\\u2022 Full Stack Web Developer Certification \\u2013 Binar Academy, Jun 2024.\\n\\u2022 Database Programming with PL\\/SQL Certification \\u2013 Oracle Academy, Jun 2023.\"},\"profil\":{\"alasan_perubahan\":\"TraKerja merekomendasikan perbaikan pada profil dengan menambahkan pengalaman dan pencapaian yang relevan, serta menekankan komitmen terhadap pembelajaran berkelanjutan. Hal ini akan memberikan gambaran yang lebih kuat tentang nilai yang dapat dibawa ke perusahaan.\",\"teks_revisi\":\"Computer Science graduate with 3+ years of experience in Software Development, Data Analytics, and Quality Assurance. Proven track record in delivering high-quality software solutions and optimizing processes. Committed to continuous learning and contributing to technology-driven business initiatives.\"},\"projek\":{\"alasan_perubahan\":\"TraKerja merekomendasikan perbaikan pada proyek dengan menambahkan action verbs yang lebih kuat dan data kuantitatif untuk menunjukkan dampak dari setiap proyek. Ini akan memberikan gambaran yang lebih jelas tentang kemampuan teknis dan hasil yang dicapai.\",\"teks_revisi\":\"**Quick Count Pilkada 2024 | Web Application | Nov 2024**\\n\\u2022 Developed a web application to display real-time quick count results, achieving a processing speed improvement of 50% compared to previous systems *[estimasi]*.\\n\\u2022 Implemented backend systems using Laravel, supporting efficient data processing for over 10,000 users during peak times *[estimasi]*.\\n\\n**Airseat | React.js, PostgreSQL | Jul 2024**\\n\\u2022 Developed a web-based airline ticket booking system, streamlining the booking process and reducing user time spent by 30% *[estimasi]*.\\n\\u2022 Created detailed system documentation, including diagrams and testing documents, ensuring clarity for future development teams.\\n\\n**InfoMATIC | Web Application | Nov 2023**\\n\\u2022 Developed an intuitive dashboard to effectively monitor and visualize students\\u2019 academic performance, improving user engagement by 40% *[estimasi]*.\\n\\u2022 Produced comprehensive system documentation, including system diagrams and testing artifacts, ensuring quality assurance and clarity for stakeholders.\\n\\n**Library Information System | Web-Based Application | Oct 2023**\\n\\u2022 Developed the system using Laravel (backend API) and Next.js (front-end), managing over 500 books and 300 members *[estimasi]*.\\n\\u2022 Created system documentation (SRS) and system design (use case and class diagrams), facilitating future enhancements and maintenance.\"},\"rencana_aksi\":[\"Langkah 1: Perbarui CV dengan menambahkan data kuantitatif pada setiap pengalaman kerja dan proyek.\",\"Langkah 2: Ganti semua bullet points dengan action verbs yang kuat dari daftar Harvard.\",\"Langkah 3: Sesuaikan profil untuk mencerminkan pengalaman dan keahlian yang relevan dengan posisi yang dilamar.\",\"Langkah 4: Tambahkan detail pada pendidikan untuk menunjukkan pencapaian akademik yang relevan.\",\"Langkah 5: Organisir keterampilan dalam kategori yang jelas untuk memudahkan penilaian.\"]}','2026-04-28 09:24:29','2026-04-28 09:24:29'),
