(274,6,'Paragon','MT CORPORATE DATA AND ANALYTICS','Seluruh Indonesia','https://paragoncorp.darwinbox.com/ms/candidatev2/main/careers/myJobs/applied?jobId=a6904230c73b87','2025-11-01',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Job Description\nPlease use the official Paragon CV template when uploading your CV.\nUsing this template is mandatory, and failure to do so may result in your application not being processed.\nYou can download the template via the link provided [Here]. Please re upload using word format.\n\nAbout the Roles:\nThe program offers practical experience in turning data into actionable insights that support strategic and operational decisions. You will explore key areas such as data analytics, data science, and data infrastructure, gaining exposure to how data is collected, processed, and transformed into valuable information. The role involves learning how to design analytical models, build reliable data systems, and deliver insights that improve business performance. This experience will help you develop a strong foundation in managing and utilizing data as a core enabler of innovation and efficiency. \n\nRequirement:\nRecent graduate from a Bachelor’s degree in Data Science, Statistics, Mathematics, Industrial Engineering, Computer Science, or related fields.\nStrong analytical and quantitative skills with the ability to interpret large datasets, identify trends, and translate data into insights.\nProficiency in Microsoft Excel / Google Sheets and familiarity with data tools such as SQL, Python, or R; experience with data visualization platforms (Tableau, Power BI, or Google Data Studio) is an advantage.\nUnderstanding of data management and interpretation techniques, including data cleaning, transformation, and validation processes.\nExcellent attention to detail and a passion for solving problems through data-driven approaches.\nStrong communication and collaboration skills, able to present findings clearly and work effectively across business and technical teams.',0,0,NULL,'2025-11-01 18:22:48','2025-12-10 12:20:48','Applied','On Process','Assessment Test','MT','Website Company'),
