(29,227,'Anandam Komputer Yogyakarta','Teknisi Komputer','Internship','Sleman, Yogyakarta','2019-01-02','2019-04-01',0,'Merakit dan mengonfigurasi perangkat komputer (hardware & basic software) sesuai kebutuhan pelanggan.\nMelakukan maintenance, service, troubleshooting, serta cleaning ke berbagai macam sistem perangkat keras komputer dan laptop.\nMembantu pengiriman atau logistik barang ke berbagai lokasi.\nMembantu pengurusan garansi atau pengembalian barang (RMA) ke distributor terkait.\n',4,'2026-04-29 09:28:15','2026-04-29 09:28:15'),
(30,229,'PT Ide Bangsa Mahardika','User Experience Specialist','Contract','Malang, Indonesia','2024-08-01','2025-11-30',0,'- Led end-to-end UI/UX design for internal enterprise application used by ±30 users, translating business workflows into structured user flows, wireframes, and high-fidelity prototypes in Figma to improve system clarity and efficiency\n- Redesigned Online Course platform by introducing 10+ new features and simplifying navigation structure, resulting in improved usability and positive user feedback\n- Conducted usability testing to identify workflow bottlenecks and refine interface architecture prior to implementation\n- Optimized company website experience (WordPress & Elementor) serving 137,000+ active users and 681,000+ tracked events, improving layout structure, content hierarchy, and navigation clarity across 5+ key pages\n- Utilized visitor insights and collaborated with 3 cross-functional departments to guide data-driven interface and content improvements',0,'2026-04-29 16:37:14','2026-04-29 16:37:14'),
